OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter after
OL,4,Cdeath of 'loving grandfather' found in
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FA 33-year-old man has been charged
OL,8,Fwith manslaughter after the death of a
OL,9,Fman found in a Leicester park.
OL,11,FJames McKeown, 62, also known as Jimmy
OL,12,Fand Spider, was found unconscious in
OL,13,FBeaumont Leys Park on Monday evening,
OL,14,Faround 6.20pm.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital but died a
OL,17,Fshort time later.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
