CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775653863
OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter after
OL,4,Cdeath of 'loving grandfather' found in
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FJoshua Moore, of Fowler Close in
OL,8,FBeaumont Leys, has been charged with
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and and is due at
OL,10,FLeicester Magistrates Court on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Mr McKeown's family
OL,14,Fdescribed him as a "loving father,
OL,15,Fbrother, partner and grandfather" who
OL,16,Fhad lived in the area for nearly 20
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,F"To say that the events of yesterday
OL,20,Fevening have changed our lives forever
OL,21,Fis an understatement," the family said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775653863
OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter after
OL,4,Cdeath of 'loving grandfather' found in
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,F"Jimmy was well known in the
OL,8,Fcommunity, affectionately known to
OL,9,Fmany as Spider. We would ask that
OL,10,Fpeople respect our privacy and give us
OL,11,Fthe time to come to terms with what
OL,12,Fhas happened."
OL,14,FLeicestershire Police is appealing for
OL,15,Fany information about the incident.
OL,17,FAn area within the park was cordoned
OL,18,Foff while officers carried out
OL,19,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
